            <title>[HTTPCLIENT-1172] LocalTestServer and supporting classes should be available as a separate jar</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HTTPCLIENT-1172</link>
                <project id="12310360" key="HTTPCLIENT">HttpComponents HttpClient</project>
                        <description>LocalTestServer and it&amp;#39;s supporting classes are useful to anyone who wants to easily &amp;quot;mock&amp;quot;/test simple http calls without having to embed a full jetty or something.&lt;br/&gt;
